ADDITIONAL DISCLAIMER FOR THIS MEDIA / ENTERTAINMENT DEMO

This project is a portfolio / educational demo only. It is NOT a real
streaming service, NOT affiliated with any actual media or OTT platform,
and does NOT stream any real movies, series, or music.

- All titles, studios, cast members, showrunners, directors, plan prices,
  account data, profile names, device names, and watchlist entries are
  FICTIONAL. Any resemblance to real titles, real people, or real services
  is coincidental.
- Named real pirate sites and torrent indexes appear in the code's safety
  regex patterns ONLY so the chatbot can correctly REFUSE requests for
  them. They are NOT endorsed, recommended, or linked to.
- Legal references mentioned in the safety layer (Indian IT Rules 2021,
  Copyright Act 1957, personality rights, MLC / ASCAP / BMI / IPRS music
  licensing, DPDP Act, COPPA, GDPR-K, etc.) are general public-domain
  information for educational context. They are NOT legal advice and
  should not be treated as such. Consult a lawyer for real-world legal
  questions.
- Fact-checking organizations named in the news-verification refusal
  block (PIB Fact Check, Alt News, BOOM, Vishvas News, Fact Crescendo,
  Snopes, PolitiFact, Reuters Fact Check, AFP Fact Check, AP Fact Check)
  are independent third parties. This project is not affiliated with any
  of them.
- The chatbot's recommendations, ratings, and IMDb scores in the
  fictional catalog are not real and should not be relied upon.

Use of this project does not grant any rights to real intellectual
property, real streaming services, or real public figures. Anyone
deploying derivatives of this code is responsible for ensuring their
content, claims, and references comply with applicable laws in their
jurisdiction.
